Subject: [PATCH 369/430] powerpc: Add I2C bus multiplexer node for B4 and
 T4240QDS

In both B4 and T4240QDS platform PCA9547 I2C bus multiplexer is used.

Change-Id: I7321bd326ef60b0462eb1faacacd52cdbd529448
Reviewed-on: http://git.am.freescale.net:8181/2414
Reviewed-by: Li Yang-R58472 <LeoLi@freescale.com>
Reviewed-by: Fleming Andrew-AFLEMING <AFLEMING@freescale.com>
Tested-by: Fleming Andrew-AFLEMING <AFLEMING@freescale.com>

[Original patch is from QorIQ-SDK-V1.4-20130625-yocto, just a minor
modification to port 3.4 kernel]
Signed-off-by: Wei Yang <Wei.Yang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/b4860qds.dts |    4 ++++
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/t4240qds.dts |    4 ++++
 2 files changed, 8 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/b4860qds.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/b4860qds.dts
index 83e2015..57fe865 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/b4860qds.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/b4860qds.dts
@@ -134,6 +134,10 @@
 		};
 
 		i2c@118000 {
+			pca9547@77 {
+				compatible = "philips,pca9547";
+				reg = <0x77>;
+			};
 			eeprom@50 {
 				compatible = "at24,24c64";
 				reg = <0x50>;
diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/t4240qds.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/t4240qds.dts
index 26ab1cd..741f9b4 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/t4240qds.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/t4240qds.dts
@@ -216,6 +216,10 @@
 		};
 
 		i2c@118000 {
+			pca9547@77 {
+				compatible = "philips,pca9547";
+				reg = <0x77>;
+			};
 			eeprom@50 {
 				compatible = "at24,24c64";
 				reg = <0x50>;
